Generate custom tailored Makefiles for your projects

Useful for C Projects that need to be repeatedly built.

To use, Try

#include <flakes.hpp> // #include <flakes/STDMakefiles/include/make.h>


int main() {
    std::makefiles::makefile s;
    s.name = "Makefile";
    s.ext = ".stdmake";

    std::makefiles::makefileconcat(s); // Returns Entire array of `s` As System Commands.
}